  // Reset to Defaults: confirm via the custom modal (same visual
  // language as the OTA monitoring dialog), then POST /api/pid/
  // reset-defaults which overwrites every pid.* key from the
  // firmware's _DEFAULT_CONFIG.  On success we repopulate the form
